import React from "react";
import { FaFacebook, FaTwitter, FaInstagram, FaYoutube} from 'react-'
import {
  FooterLinksContainer,
  FooterLinksWrapper,
  FooterLinksItems,
  FooterLink,
} from "./FooterElements";

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <FooterLinksContainer>
      <FooterLinksWrapper>
        <FooterLinksItems>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Account and Billing</FooterLink>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Plans and Pricing</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinksItems>
        <FooterLinksItems>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">FAQ</FooterLink>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Help Center</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinksItems>
        <FooterLinksItems>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Privacy</FooterLink>
          <FooterLink to="/faq">Terms of Use</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinksItems>
      </FooterLinksWrapper>
      <SocialMedia>
        <SocialMediaWrap>
          <SocialLogo to="/">
            <SocialIcon />
            MOVIEFLIX
          </SocialLogo>
          <WebsiteRights>MOVIEFLIX Â© 2020</WebsiteRights>
          <SocialIcons>
            <SocialIconLink
              href="/"
              target="_blank"
              aria-label="FaFacebook"
            ></SocialIconLink>
            <SocialIconLink
              href="/"
              target="_blank"
              aria-label="FaTwitter"
            ></SocialIconLink>
            <SocialIconLink
              href="/"
              target="_blank"
              aria-label="FaYoutube"
            ></SocialIconLink>
            <SocialIconLink
              href="/"
              target="_blank"
              aria-label="FaInstagram"
            ></SocialIconLink>
          </SocialIcons>
        </SocialMediaWrap>
      </SocialMedia>
    </FooterLinksContainer>
  );
};

export default Footer;
